		    =-=-=- Necromancer -=-=-=

	Also known as a Death-Mage, the Necromancer is a
hybrid spell caster. A Necromancer gains his power from
the realm of the dead, through summoning, communing with,
and control of the dead. His spells focus on death, cold,
and undeath. Drain life, and wind of death are typical
Necromancy spells.

Type:   Death/Undeath Spell Caster
Skills: Limited combat
Spells: Undead Summoning, Drain, Cold Attacks
Prime Attributes: Int, Wis

Comments: The necromancers have the most summoning spells in
	the MUD. There whole existence revolves around their
	powerful pets, which are the focus of the majority of
	their spells.
